I"´<p>We strongly believe that current Augmented Reality technologies can im- prove significantly the user experience on the early design process stages. Augmented Reality has the power to visualize any data that we want in the real world. In particular, Microsoft HoloLens seems to be a good candidate. Therefore, the main goal of this Interdisciplinary Project is the integration of HoloLens devices to the CDP platform. This mean that users can see and interact with the virtual scene directly on top of the projection surface.</p>

